{{{
SELECT sd.sealevel, lr.a * sd.sealevel + lr.b FROM
   (SELECT    (S.n*S.sum_xy - S.sum_y * S.sum_x ) / ( S.n * S.sum_sqr_x - S.sum_x * S.sum_x ) as a,        
      ( S.sum_y * S.sum_sqr_x - S.sum_x * S.sum_xy ) / ( S.n * S.sum_sqr_x - S.sum_x * S.sum_x ) as b 
   FROM (SELECT COUNT( S.sealevel) as n, SUM( S.sv ) as sum_xy, 
      SUM( S.sealevel ) as sum_x, SUM(S.voltage ) as sum_y, SUM(S.sealevel * S.sealevel ) as sum_sqr_x    
         FROM ( SELECT seaLevel, voltage, seaLevel*voltage 
            FROM SeaDefenceEast[FROM NOW TO NOW SLIDE 5000 seconds] ) S ) S ) lr, 
   seadefence[now] sd;
}}}
